<!--
review_mode    : off | lenient | strict   (default off — speed-first)
   off     → no reviewer dispatched
   lenient → spec-reviewer only
   strict  → spec-reviewer → quality-reviewer

security_review : off | diff | full       (default off)
   off  → no security reviewer
   diff → security-reviewer scoped to this ticket's diff
   full → security-reviewer scans whole worktree

Both fields are proposed by /hfx:plan Step 6.5 only if the plan touches
a risky surface (auth/secrets/CI/prompts). For a normal ticket they
stay at `off` so /hfx:run executes at full speed.
-->


